sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant T as Telegram Interface
    participant P as Planning Service
    participant J as Job Dispatcher
    participant W as Worker
    participant L as LLM Providers

    U->>T: Send prompt
    T->>P: Draft plan
    P-->>T: Plan with questions, design, and test approach
    T-->>U: Plan for approval with run ID and estimate
    U->>T: /approve <run_id>
    T->>J: Dispatch approved run
    J-->>T: Run queued
    J->>W: Start background execution
    W->>L: Design, code, test, and review stages
    W-->>T: Progress update
    T-->>U: Stage update
    L-->>W: Final reviewed result
    W-->>T: Completion or failure
    T-->>U: Final response